32:51.051 --> 32:55.275
it's that you never know
what people are capable of.

32:55.942 --> 32:58.474
I'm sorry, I'm sorry, I can't
answer that at this time.

32:58.476 --> 33:00.279
Let's see how
the investigation unfolds.

33:00.281 --> 33:01.584
Why would I tell you
my strategy?

33:01.586 --> 33:02.583
Quebert's manuscript was
found with the body...

33:02.585 --> 33:05.310
The manuscript
doesn't prove a thing!

33:05.312 --> 33:08.074
Writing isn't killing!
Write that down.

33:08.076 --> 33:08.880
Even your writing.

33:08.882 --> 33:10.877
Excuse me, guys.
Sorry.

33:13.221 --> 33:14.909
- I... I...
- No comment! No comment!

33:14.911 --> 33:17.789
He's got no comment!

33:17.791 --> 33:19.402
Thank you,
ladies and gentlemen!

33:19.404 --> 33:20.861
Thank you!

33:20.863 --> 33:22.436
Now, listen to me!

33:22.438 --> 33:25.393
I got two words for you:
"Shut the fuck up!"

33:25.395 --> 33:26.890
The slightest thing
you say can...

33:26.892 --> 33:28.272
can be used against us

33:28.274 --> 33:29.270
and ruin my defense.

33:29.272 --> 33:30.384
What is
your defense?

33:30.386 --> 33:32.227
Deny, deny, deny!

33:32.229 --> 33:33.341
The relationship,

33:33.343 --> 33:34.724
the kidnappings, the murder.

33:34.726 --> 33:36.490
It's all circumstantial.

33:36.492 --> 33:38.563
We're gonna plead not guilty,

33:38.565 --> 33:39.908
Harry's gonna get acquitted,

33:39.910 --> 33:42.365
and I'm gonna counter-sue
for millions of dollars.

33:42.367 --> 33:44.287
Yup?

33:44.940 --> 33:45.859
Thanks, man.

33:45.861 --> 33:48.125
Talk to the nice
townsfolk.

33:48.127 --> 33:49.968
Those hicks are
potential witnesses.

33:49.970 --> 33:51.658
Find out who's got
a drinking problem,

33:51.660 --> 33:53.655
who beats his wife,
who owes money,

33:53.657 --> 33:55.729
because a witness
who drinks

33:55.731 --> 33:56.765
or beats his wife

33:56.767 --> 33:58.301
is not
a credible witness.

33:58.303 --> 33:59.683
Find all the dirt
you can.

34:01.298 --> 34:02.103
A bit of a despicable
approach,

34:02.105 --> 34:03.216
don't you think?

34:03.218 --> 34:05.098
You want your best friend
to go free?

34:06.252 --> 34:07.095
Roth. Go.

34:07.097 --> 34:09.016
<i>CNN called.</i>

34:10.360 --> 34:12.281
Holy shit...

34:12.588 --> 34:14.735
Oh, my God.

34:14.737 --> 34:16.349
Hey, we're gonna
get you out of here.

34:16.351 --> 34:17.847
Okay?

34:17.849 --> 34:19.768
Yeah, it's just...

34:21.496 --> 34:23.223
Don't show it to Roth.

34:23.225 --> 34:24.335
Yeah.

34:24.338 --> 34:26.255
It's going to be
okay, Harry, okay?

34:26.257 --> 34:27.178
Well, I've been
watching the news.

34:27.179 --> 34:28.675
I know what they're saying.

34:28.677 --> 34:30.556
My career is over,
my life is over.

34:30.559 --> 34:32.746
It's the big fall.
I am falling.

34:32.748 --> 34:35.088
Yeah, well, you know,
a wise man once told me

34:35.090 --> 34:36.777
that you should never
be afraid of falling.

34:36.780 --> 34:38.007
Yeah, not so wise
after all,

34:38.009 --> 34:39.158
but thank you for coming.

34:39.159 --> 34:40.119
Yeah, of course,
of course.

34:40.121 --> 34:41.539
I'm staying
at Goose Cove.

34:41.541 --> 34:44.304
Right?
I fed the seagulls.

34:44.306 --> 34:46.033
You should go back to New York.

34:46.034 --> 34:47.645
Look, Roth is gonna
get you off, okay?

34:47.647 --> 34:48.835
But until he does,

34:48.837 --> 34:50.487
I'm gonna stay and do
whatever I can to help.

34:50.489 --> 34:51.677
What about your novel?

34:51.679 --> 34:53.329
Don't worry
about the novel.

34:53.331 --> 34:56.822
Listen, what you said
on the phone when you called me?

34:56.824 --> 34:58.474
You asked
what you had done to Nola.

34:58.476 --> 35:00.548
You said it was
your fault.

35:00.550 --> 35:03.697
Yeah, well, it was just
the emotion, and...

35:03.699 --> 35:07.229
and you were the only one
who knew about Nola, so I...

35:07.231 --> 35:09.801
All right, look, a lot of...
a lot of rage,

35:09.803 --> 35:11.530
and innuendo,

35:11.532 --> 35:14.103
but... no hard evidence

35:14.105 --> 35:16.752
that directly implicates you
in the girl's murder.

35:16.754 --> 35:18.674
Yet.

35:19.596 --> 35:21.821
I don't like
surprises.

35:21.823 --> 35:24.548
Is there anything
that you haven't told me

35:24.550 --> 35:25.700
about you and Nola?

35:25.702 --> 35:28.004
Because I need
to know everything

35:28.006 --> 35:29.616
if I'm gonna
represent you properly.

35:29.618 --> 35:31.344
Mm-hmm.

35:31.346 --> 35:33.341
The police asked me
what I was doing

35:33.343 --> 35:37.143
the evening of... August 30th.

35:37.145 --> 35:38.487
I told them
I was out of town,

35:38.489 --> 35:40.524
I was in Boston.

35:41.638 --> 35:42.711
I wasn't.

35:42.713 --> 35:46.090
I was in a motel
off of Shore Road,

35:46.092 --> 35:48.012
<i>the By the Sea Motel.</i>

35:51.276 --> 35:54.077
By 9:00,
she hadn't arrived.

35:54.079 --> 35:54.999
That was unlike her,

35:55.001 --> 35:56.920
because she was
always on time.

35:58.725 --> 36:00.950
<i>"Room 8 at 8:00.</i>

36:00.952 --> 36:02.679
<i>Then away forever.</i>

36:02.681 --> 36:04.601
<i>Love, N."</i>

36:08.018 --> 36:09.744
I don't know what time
I fell asleep waiting for her,

36:09.746 --> 36:13.123
but I woke up to the radio,

36:13.125 --> 36:15.120
and that's when I...

36:15.122 --> 36:18.499
I found out she was missing.

36:18.501 --> 36:21.610
She was wearing her red dress.

36:21.612 --> 36:23.108
She wore that for me.

36:23.110 --> 36:25.142
It was her favorite dress.

36:25.144 --> 36:26.755
<i>Good morning! It's 6:30,</i>

36:26.757 --> 36:29.751
<i>and the forecast is sunny
for this Sunday, August 31st.</i>

36:29.753 --> 36:32.016
<i>And now, an urgent report.</i>

36:32.018 --> 36:33.668
<i>Police issued a general alert</i>

36:33.670 --> 36:35.203
<i>in the Sommerdale region</i>

36:35.205 --> 36:38.199
<i>after the disappearance
of 15-year-old Nola Kellergan</i>

36:38.201 --> 36:40.848
<i>yesterday evening
around 7:00 p.m.</i>

36:40.850 --> 36:42.231
<i>Police would like to hear
from anyone</i>

36:42.233 --> 36:44.228
<i>with information about
the girl's whereabouts.</i>

36:44.230 --> 36:45.687
<i>At the time she disappeared,</i>

36:45.689 --> 36:47.685
<i>Nola Kellergan
was wearing a red dress.</i>

36:49.836 --> 36:52.099
So, you were meeting.

36:52.101 --> 36:54.021
You were meeting to...

36:54.943 --> 36:56.785
We were gonna leave town.

36:56.787 --> 36:59.088
Okay...

36:59.090 --> 37:00.279
and that's why

37:00.281 --> 37:02.508
you said it was
your fault?

37:03.851 --> 37:05.309
Mm-hmm.

37:05.311 --> 37:07.690
I know
how it looks,

37:07.692 --> 37:09.763
but I didn't
kill Nola.

37:09.765 --> 37:10.685
I loved her,

37:10.687 --> 37:11.837
and if I hadn't
have asked her

37:11.839 --> 37:13.027
to meet me
at that motel,

37:13.029 --> 37:14.949
she might still
be alive today.

37:21.170 --> 37:23.090
I don't think
you get it.

37:24.434 --> 37:26.276
It's a fucking disaster.

37:26.278 --> 37:27.696
If the prosecution
gets hold of this,

37:27.698 --> 37:29.657
Harry is screwed.

37:32.537 --> 37:34.457
Ah, shit...

37:42.290 --> 37:44.400
<i>"On my desk,
there's a porcelain pot.</i>

37:44.402 --> 37:46.627
<i>Inside is a key to my locker
at the gym in Montburry,</i>

37:46.629 --> 37:48.087
<i>203.</i>

37:48.089 --> 37:49.392
<i>Everything is in there.</i>

37:49.394 --> 37:50.621
<i>Burn it all.</i>

37:50.623 --> 37:52.543
<i>I'm in danger."</i>

38:47.416 --> 38:50.871
It's "The Origin of Evil."

38:50.873 --> 38:53.637
It's Harry's
original manuscript.

38:55.097 --> 38:57.094
Holy cow...

39:08.076 --> 39:10.800
<i>I knew
what I was doing was illegal,</i>

39:10.802 --> 39:14.141
<i>that by burning all this
incriminating evidence,</i>

39:14.143 --> 39:17.750
<i>I was suddenly an accomplice.</i>

39:17.752 --> 39:21.322
<i>But I also knew Harry,</i>

39:21.324 --> 39:24.854
<i>and he was my teacher,
my mentor.</i>

39:24.856 --> 39:27.273
<i>He was my friend,</i>

39:27.275 --> 39:29.196
<i>and I had to help him.</i>

39:30.156 --> 39:31.728
<i>There was no way
he could have done</i>

39:31.730 --> 39:34.956
<i>what he was accused of doing.</i>

39:46.130 --> 39:47.549
<i>Then,</i>

39:47.551 --> 39:51.082
<i>as I watched the flames
turn paper to ash,</i>

39:51.084 --> 39:54.115
<i>a chilling thought
crept over me...</i>

39:54.117 --> 39:58.149
<i>What if I was wrong?</i>

40:09.439 --> 40:11.973
<i>Was I in danger myself?</i>

